air quality alerts

read_alert.Rd

read air quality alerts issued by airparif.

read_alert()

Value

a data.frame with the following columns:

  • date_time: (POSIXct with time zone set to Europe/Paris), date-time of measurement

  • pollutant: (character), pollutant whose level has triggered the alert

  • state: (character), state of the alert, a label meaning information and alert - coded as c("Niveau d'information et de recommandation or alert", "Niveau d'alerte").

See also

Other functions about Paris air quality: read_atmo, read_measures

Examples

if( is_magellan_available() ){
  read_alert()
}
